---
// cenno — Privacy Policy. Standalone legal page; styling inherits the site tokens.
import "../styles/tokens.css";

const TITLE = "cenno — Privacy Policy";
const DESCRIPTION =
  "Cenno Companion collects no personal data. Prompts sync through your own private iCloud; the developer has no access.";
const UPDATED = "18 June 2026";
const CONTACT = "glebis@gmail.com";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{TITLE}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={DESCRIPTION} />
    <meta name="robots" content="index,follow" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://cenno.salient.community/privacy" />
  </head>
  <body class="legal">
    <main class="legal-wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow"><a href="/">← cenno</a></p>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: {UPDATED}</p>

      <p>
        Cenno Companion (the “App”) is an iPhone and Apple Watch app that displays
        prompts from your own AI agents and lets you answer them. This policy explains
        how the App handles your information. In short: <strong>the App collects no
        personal data, and the developer has no access to your content.</strong>
      </p>

      <h2>Data we collect</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>None.</strong> The developer does not collect, store, sell, or share any
        personal data from the App. There is no analytics, no advertising, no tracking,
        and no third-party SDKs embedded in the App.
      </p>

      <h2>How your prompts are handled</h2>
      <p>
        Prompts and your answers sync between your own devices through
        <strong>Apple iCloud (CloudKit), in your private database</strong>. This data
        lives in your personal iCloud account under your control. The developer cannot
        access, read, or retain it. Apple’s handling of iCloud data is governed by
        <a href="https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/">Apple’s Privacy Policy</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Notifications</h2>
      <p>
        The App uses Apple Push Notification service (APNs) to alert you when a new
        prompt is waiting. Push delivery is operated by Apple; the developer does not
        receive or store the contents of those notifications.
      </p>

      <h2>Children’s privacy</h2>
      <p>
        The App is not directed to children and does not knowingly collect any
        information from anyone, regardless of age.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>
        If this policy changes, the updated version will be posted at this URL with a
        new “Last updated” date.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about privacy? Email <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT}`}>{CONTACT}</a>.
      </p>

      <p class="legal-foot"><a href="/impressum">Impressum</a> · <a href="/">cenno.salient.community</a></p>
    </main>

    <style>
      .legal {
        margin: 0;
        background: var(--cenno-color-paper, #fff);
        color: var(--cenno-color-text-default, #1d1d1f);
        font-family: var(--cenno-font-family-default, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif);
        line-height: var(--cenno-font-leading-body, 1.6);
      }
      .legal-wrap {
        max-width: 720px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: clamp(32px, 6vw, 72px) 24px 96px;
      }
      .eyebrow {
        font-size: 14px;
        text-transform: lowercase;
        letter-spacing: var(--cenno-font-tracking-caption, 0.02em);
        color: var(--cenno-color-text-dim, #86868b);
        margin: 0 0 24px;
      }
      .eyebrow a, .legal-foot a, main a { color: var(--cenno-color-flow-reminder, #0a84ff); }
      h1 { font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 38px); letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 0 0 4px; }
      h2 { font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin: 40px 0 8px; }
      .updated { color: var(--cenno-color-text-dim, #86868b); font-size: 15px; margin: 0 0 32px; }
      p { margin: 0 0 14px; }
      .legal-foot {
        margin-top: 56px;
        padding-top: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--cenno-color-line, #e5e5e7);
        font-size: 14px;
        color: var(--cenno-color-text-dim, #86868b);
      }
    </style>
  </body>
</html>
